{"lemma":"غَيْبُ","slug":"غَيْبُ","root":"غ.#.ب","root_slug":"غ-_-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-_-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"غَيْب","root":"غيب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":49},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n32684","n32685"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غَابَ (ḡāba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"that which is unseen, unperceived, unwitnessed, yet to be seen","examples":[{"text":"اَلَّذِينَ يُؤْمِنُونَ بِالغَيْبِ وَيُقِيمُونَ الصَّلَاةَ وَمِمَّا رَزَقْنَاهُم يُنْفِقُونَ","english":"Those who trust in \"what has yet to be seen\", those who cause the keeping up of close connection [to God], and from what We have given them they cause to be dispensed."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣajb/","/ɣiː.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32684","headword_ar":"غَيْبٌ","root":"gyb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Whatever is absent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hidden, from one;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K, TA;) as though it were an inf. n. used in the sense of the act. part. n. [in which the meaning of a subst. is predominant]; (TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAy^ibN","text_ar":"غَايِبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", which [in this sense] is a subst., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAhilN","text_ar":"كَاهِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) or an act. part. n. used in the sense of a subst.: (MF:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything that is absent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hidden, from the eyes; invisible, unseen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unapparent; whether it be,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be not, perceived in the heart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything unperceivable; absent from the range,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beyond the reach, of perception by sense,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of mental perception;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"undiscoverable unless by means of divine revelation; a mystery,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"secret, such as an event of futurity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing that has been hidden from men, and with which the Prophet has acquainted them, of the events of the resurrection and of Paradise and of Hell &c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"thus in the Kur ii. 2; (Zj, TA;) and [hence] Zj explains"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algayob","text_ar":"الغَيْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning, in the Kur lxxxi. 24,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that which has been revealed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dn","text_ar":"ضن"},{"kind":"text","text":":) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guyuwbN","text_ar":"غُيُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) [See also the Ksh and Bd in ii. 2.] [Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAlamu Algayobi","text_ar":"عَالَمُ الغَيْبِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The world of the unseen; the invisible world."},{"kind":"text","text":"] And [hence also] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajama","text_ar":"رَجَمَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlgayobi","text_ar":"بِالغَيْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qa*afa biAlgayobi","text_ar":"قَذَفَ بِالغَيْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"q*f","text_ar":"قذف"},{"kind":"text","text":")]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spoke of that which he did not know:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 494:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaAla rajomFA biAlgayobi","text_ar":"قَالَ رَجْمًا بِالغَيْبِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He said conjecturally,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speaking of that which was hidden from him"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unknown by him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without evidence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without proof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rjm","text_ar":"رجم"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.) ―         -b2-  And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Doubt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a doubting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) but some disapprove this: some regard it as tropical: and some pronounce it correct: (MF, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giyaAbN","text_ar":"غِيَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guyuwbN","text_ar":"غُيُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) A poet says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"A^anota nabiY~N taEolamu AlgiyaAbaA\n                      \n                     \n                        laA qaAy^ilFA A_ifokFA walaA murotaAbaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou art a prophet, knowing doubts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"things doubted; not saying a lie, nor a thing suspected:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, more probably, the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the things unseen"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place, in the ground, that hides,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conceals, one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a low,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depressed, place in the ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a tract of land:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any place such that one knows not what is in it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place such that one knows not what is behind it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guyuwbN","text_ar":"غُيُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) Hence the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano Zahori gayobK","text_ar":"عَنْ ظَهْرِ غَيْبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a verse of Lebeed cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZahorN","text_ar":"ظَهْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (TA.) [Hence also] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samiEotu SawotFA mino waraA='i Algayobi","text_ar":"سَمِعْتُ صَوْتًا مِنْ وَرَا=ءِ الغَيْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I heard a sound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"voice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place that I saw not."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tanaAwalahu","text_ar":"تَنَاوَلَهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biZahori Algayobi bimaA yasuww^uhu","text_ar":"بِظَهْرِ الغَيْبِ بِمَا يَسُووُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 8. And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"takal~ama bihi Eano","text_ar":"تَكَلَّمَ بِهِ عَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zahori gayobK","text_ar":"ظَهْرِ غَيْبٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano Zahori Algayobi","text_ar":"عَنْ ظَهْرِ الغَيْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, and A and O in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zhr","text_ar":"ظهر"},{"kind":"text","text":") [app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spoke of it by memory; in the absence of a book"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as one says in modern Arabic,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY AlgaAy^ib","text_ar":"عَلَى الغَايِب"},{"kind":"text","text":". See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZahorN","text_ar":"ظَهْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-  Also The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamoSap","text_ar":"خَمْصَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pit,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depression,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as is shown by what here follows, (thus in the A, and in the Ksh in ii. 2, in the TA"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huforap","text_ar":"حُفْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", which has a similar meaning,)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is in the place where the kidney is situate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ksh, A, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and which swells up when the beast becomes big in the belly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so says ISh: (Ksh ubi suprà:) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xamoSap","text_ar":"خَمْصَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is next to the kidney:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in ii. 2: [De Sacy doubted respecting its meaning, but conjectured that it might be thus: see his Anthol. Gramm. Arabe p. 55:]) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guyuwbN","text_ar":"غُيُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aribati Ald~aAb~apu Hat~aY","text_ar":"شَرِبَتِ الدَّابَّةُ حَتَّى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waArato guyuwba kulaAhaA","text_ar":"وَارَتْ غُيُوبَ كُلَاهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISh, Ksh ubi suprà, A, TA,) meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huzuwmahaA","text_ar":"هُزُومَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beast drank until it concealed the pits of its kidneys"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fat of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"varob","text_ar":"ثَرْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] of a sheep or goat: so called because it is hidden from the eye. (TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAy^ibN","text_ar":"غَايِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["K","TA","MF","IAar","S","Sh","A","Ksh"]},{"entry_id":"n32685","headword_ar":"غَيَبٌ","root":"gyb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAy^ibN","text_ar":"غَايِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}